Mail On Sunday Free CD
______________________

Songbook is a compilation album by English pop 
singer Robbie Williams. 

The album is free, but it is limited edition only. 
As he launches his comeback, Robbie Williams is 
giving away this exclusive CD featuring his greatest 
hits for free inside for weekend newspaper 
The Mail on Sunday on October 11, 2009.

Featuring 12 classic Robbie Williams tracks, 
the CD includes live recordings from Slane Castle, 
Koln, London's The Forum and, of course, Knebworth.
